½In Loving Memory of Trevor J Currie
20.9.1944~26.5.2020
Loving Husband, Dad, Grandad & Brother
Your life gave us treasured memories
Loved beyond words - missed forever"╝
╣REMEMBERING KEITH HARWOOD
ENJOYED LIFE AND LIVED IT TO THE FULL
YOU SPREAD SO MUCH HAPPINESS ALONG THE WAY
YOU MADE EVERYONE FEEL SPECIAL
YOUR SMILE SAID IT ALL, LOVED AND MISSED ALWAYS"▐
█Barbara Joan Bowman
Born 14th May 1928
Died 23rd November 2011
My one and only love for 67 years
Till we meet again, George

George Roland Bowman
Born 30th January 1927
