ķMAUREEN 'MEMOW' PILKINGTON
1929-2023
LANCASTRIAN NATIVE BUT CALLED SANDGATE AND
FOLKESTONE HER HOME FOR SO LONG.
BELOVED MOTHER, GRANDMOTHER AND FRIEND TO SO MANY.
DOG LOVER OF MUTLEY, TILLY AND FREDDIE.

DAVID D. SIMPSON
1928-2023
A FOLKESTONE MAN BORN AND BRED.
DEAR BROTHER, GODFATHER AND
GREAT FRIEND TO MEMOW.
